SmartCode Internet Solutions

We Build Smart Solutions Since 2008

Being a premium web development company in Dubai, our focus lies on speed, innovation, and quality of services. We excel at providing comprehensive developments and aim for gleaning happy customers by offering timely and stellar business solutions ensured by our highly accomplished web-developers.
Our Services

What We Do

Advanced and user-friendly Mobile application and Website for your business. From automation to education we develop solutions for every type of industry out there

E-Commerce

E-Commerce

Retail, groceries, organic stores, electronics, fashion, apparels, and other online stores.

Real Estate

Search, buy and sell properties, brokerage, promoters, realtors, research, marketing and CRM.

Education

E-learning, audio video learning room, online exams, students and staff management solutions.

Health Care

Doctors appointment booking, hospital management, online pharmacy.

Industries

Industry-specific, inventory management, supply chain management and logistics.

Food

Online food delivery, ERP and inventory management for the food industry.

How It Works

Getting online is easy. Succeeding online is a different story. You need more than just a beautiful website to stand out these days. we can build strong website and applications for all platforms.

Strategy

We define your competition and target audience. Discover what is working in your online industry, then design your website accordingly.

Develop

We turn your ideas into a reality. &our website is placed on a "development server" where you get to watch the whole process, live.

Support

This is where you go live, to the world. Design, marketing, and maintenance; we'll be at your side for the life of your site.

Applications & Partners

Since 2008 we have been designing and building websites for clients throughout the Middle east. smartcode internet solutions provides an in-house team of dedicated designers and developers that have worked on websites of all sizes

من هو عبد الرحمن حسين|وهو مدير وشريك مؤسس لـ”شركة سمارت كود لحلول الإنترنت“ منذ 2008 في الإمارات العربية المتحدة. شغل منصب مدير الإعلام الرقمي في ”مجلة فوربس الشرق الأوسط“ بين 2011 و2012، وعمل كمطور أول ويب في ”شركة أمانة كابيتال“ 2012 و2015، ومطور ويب في كل من ”شركة فلاغ شيب“ 2008 و2012، و”موقع سيريا نيوز“ خلال 2008.
